==English==

===Transitive verb===
'''to belay'''
#(''nautical'') to make a [[rope]] [[fast]] by [[turning]] it round a [[cleat]] or [[belaying pin]]
# the [[general]] to [[stop]] or [[cease]]
#(''climbing'') to [[secure]] a [[climber]] at the end of a rope

==Noun==
'''belay'''
#(''climbing'') The securing of a rope to a [[rock]] or other [[projection]]; the [[object]] to which the rope is secured

